{
  "description": "A nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated with bright lights, dominated by a prominent bridge and fireworks. The bridge, appearing white with glowing lights, stretches across dark water. Behind it, a city skyline rises with tall buildings, several of which are lit up in various colors, including blue and gold. Fireworks explode in the air above the skyline, appearing as bright pink/red streaks.  Trees and hills can be seen in the midground, partially obscuring the base of some buildings. In the distant background, another bridge structure is visible, also illuminated. The overall scene is vibrant and conveys a sense of celebration.",
